#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prints the current zoomed view."
msgstr "वर्तमानं जूम कृतं दृश्यं मुद्रयति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
